ed="T" n="0857c12"/><anchor n="T.50.2061.0857c12"/><head><date from-iso="+0936-12-05" key="j20632662067017" to-iso="+0947-03-14">晉</date><placeName key="PL000000003784"><placeName>太原</placeName><placeName>永和</placeName><placeName>三學院</placeName></placeName><persName key="A009945">息塵</persName>傳</head><p><lb
ed="T" n="0857c13"/><persName key="A009945">釋息塵</persName>，姓<name>楊</name>氏，<placeName key="PL000000003794">并州</placeName>人也。父遷貿有無，營<lb
ed="T" n="0857c14"/>利而已。其母氏甞夢人服裝偉麗，稱寄宵<lb
ed="T" n="0857c15"/>宿，便覺娠妊。生而有異，童稚不群。每聞鐘<lb
ed="T" n="0857c16"/>唄之音，凝神側耳。年方十二，因夢金<anchor xml:id="beg0857sgsz21"/>人<anchor xml:id="end0857sgsz21"/>瑰<lb
ed="T" n="0857c17"/>奇之狀，引之入精廬。明旦告白二親，懇求<lb
ed="T" n="0857c18"/>出家。未允之前，泣而不食。父母憫其天然，<lb
ed="T" n="0857c19"/>情何厭塞，遂曲順之。即投<placeName key="PL000000059401">草堂院</placeName>，從師誦<lb
ed="T" n="0857c20"/>《淨名經》、《菩薩戒》<ptr target="#n54"/>，達宵不寐。將周一祀<ptr type="glossary" target="#g1230"/>，捨本<lb
ed="T" n="0857c21"/>諷通。年當十七，便聽習維摩講席，粗知大<lb
ed="T" n="0857c22"/>義。及乎弱冠，乃圓上品<ptr type="glossary" target="#g289"/>，執持律範，曾無缺<lb
ed="T" n="0857c23"/>然。年二十三，文義斡通，於<placeName key="PL000000003781">崇福寺</placeName><ptr rend="display:none;" target="#n2930"/><persName key="A013461">宗感<roleName>法師</roleName></persName><lb
ed="T" n="0857c24"/>勝集傳授。復學因明<ptr target="#n801"/>、唯識<ptr target="#n2928"/>，不虧敷演，學徒<lb
ed="T" n="0857c25"/>頴脫者數人。<placeName key="PL000000003781">崇福寺</placeName><persName key="A013464"><persName>辯才大師</persName><persName>從式</persName></persName>最為高<lb
ed="T" n="0857c26"/>足。於<date key="j20516472052001" notAfter-iso="+0906-02-01" notBefore-iso="+0905-02-12"><name>天祐</name>二年</date>，<persName key="A009891">李<roleName>氏</roleName></persName>奄有<placeName key="PL000000005198">河東</placeName>，<persName key="A009891">武皇帝</persName>請<lb
ed="T" n="0857c27"/>居<placeName key="PL000000003786"><placeName>大安寺</placeName><placeName>淨土院</placeName></placeName>，四事供養<ptr type="glossary" target="#g1914"/>。專覽藏教<ptr type="glossary" target="#g1915"/>，<anchor xml:id="beg0857002"/>修<lb
ed="T" n="0857c28"/>鍊<anchor xml:id="end0857002"/><ptr type="glossary" target="#g75"/>上生業<ptr target="#n1052"/>，設無遮<ptr type="glossary" target="#g379"/>大齋，前後五會。<persName key="A009945">塵</persName>甞以<lb
ed="T" n="0857c29"/>身飼狼虎，入山谷中，其獸近嗅而奔走。又<pb ed="T" n="0858a" xml:id="T50.2061.0858a"/><lb
ed="T" n="0858a01"/>於林薄<ptr type="glossary" target="#g1910"/>裸體，以啖蚊虻。乃遊<placeName key="PL000000028989"><placeName>仙巖</placeName><placeName>嶽寺</placeName></placeName>，養<lb
ed="T" n="0858a02"/>道棲神。復看大藏經匝，設齋，然一指，伸<lb
ed="T" n="0858a03"/>其報慶。<ref type="place" target="#PL000000028989">彼寺</ref>有聖<persName key="A002803">觀音菩薩</persName>像，長爥七燈，<lb
ed="T" n="0858a04"/>香<anchor xml:id="beg0858sgsz1"/>華<anchor xml:id="end0858sgsz1"/>供獻。後被諸生就請下山，城內傳揚<lb
ed="T" n="0858a05"/>大論<ptr target="#n55"/>，四序無輟。逐月設沐浴，臨河就沼，投<lb
ed="T" n="0858a06"/>飼水族；以<anchor xml:id="beg0858sgsz3"/>己<anchor xml:id="end0858sgsz3"/>噠嚫<ptr type="glossary" target="#g1276"/>，旋贖羽毛──沈潛高明<ptr type="glossary" target="#g1916"/>，以<lb
ed="T" n="0858a07"/>遂生性。或施牢獄人食，或賑惠貧乏，或捐<lb
ed="T" n="0858a08"/><anchor xml:id="beg0858001"/>旛<anchor xml:id="end0858001"/>蓋於<placeName key="PL000000059235">淨明</placeName>、<placeName key="PL000000059054">金藏</placeName>二塔。<placeName key="PL000000057656">後唐</placeName><date key="j20611272061509" from-iso="+0932-02-13" to-iso="+0931-01-27"><name>長興</name>二年</date>，眾請<lb
ed="T" n="0858a09"/>於<placeName key="PL000000005907">大安國寺</placeName>後建<placeName key="PL000000003784">三學院</placeName>一所，供待四方<lb
ed="T" n="0858a10"/>聽眾。時又講華嚴新經<ptr target="#n2156"/>，傳授於<placeName key="PL000000003781">崇福寺</placeName><persName key="A013467">繼暉<lb
ed="T" n="0858a11"/><roleName>法師</roleName></persName>。由是三年不出院門，一字一<anchor xml:id="beg0858sgsz5"/>禮<anchor xml:id="end0858sgsz5"/>《華嚴<lb
ed="T" n="0858a12"/>經》一遍，字字<anchor xml:id="beg0858sgsz7"/>禮<anchor xml:id="end0858sgsz7"/>大佛名經<ptr target="#n1001"/>，共一百二十卷。復<lb
ed="T" n="0858a13"/><anchor xml:id="beg0858002"/>煉<anchor xml:id="end0858002"/>一指，前後計然五指。時<persName key="A006579">晉高祖</persName>潛躍<placeName key="PL000000003731">晉<lb
ed="T" n="0858a14"/>陽</placeName>，最多欽重。洎乎龍飛，<persName key="A009945">塵</persName>每入<placeName key="PL000000023638">洛京</placeName>朝覲，<lb
ed="T" n="0858a15"/>必延內殿從容<ptr type="glossary" target="#g1410"/>，錫賚頗豐。<ref type="person" target="#A006579">帝</ref>賜紫服并懿<lb
ed="T" n="0858a16"/>號，固讓方俞。<persName key="A009945">塵</persName>聞<placeName key="PL000000042886"><placeName>鳳翔府</placeName><placeName>法門寺</placeName></placeName>有佛中指<lb
ed="T" n="0858a17"/>骨節真身，乃辭<ref type="person" target="#A006579">帝</ref>往<placeName key="PL000000042847"><anchor xml:id="beg0858sgsz9"/>岐<anchor xml:id="end0858sgsz9"/>陽</placeName>瞻<anchor xml:id="beg0858sgsz11"/>禮<anchor xml:id="end0858sgsz11"/>，覩其希奇，<lb
ed="T" n="0858a18"/>又然一指。<persName key="A009945">塵</persName>之雙手唯存二指耳。續於<placeName key="PL000000042792">天<lb
ed="T" n="0858a19"/>柱寺</placeName>，就<persName key="A013469">楚倫<roleName>法師</roleName></persName>學《俱舍論》<ptr target="#n1429"/>。方經數日，微<lb
ed="T" n="0858a20"/>有疾生，至七月二十七日辰時<ptr target="#n2929"/>枕肱而逝，<lb
ed="T" n="0858a21"/>俗年六十三，臘四十四。平常唯衣大布，不<lb
ed="T" n="0858a22"/>蓄盈長。六時<anchor xml:id="beg0858sgsz13"/>禮<anchor xml:id="end0858sgsz13"/>佛，未曾少缺。<placeName key="PL000000047360">隴坻</placeName>之間聞<lb
ed="T" n="0858a23"/>其示滅，黑白二眾具威儀送焚之，得舍利<lb
ed="T" n="0858a24"/>數百粒。弟子以靈骨歸于<placeName key="PL000000003794">太原</placeName>，<persName key="A006579">晉祖</persName>勅葬<lb
ed="T" n="0858a25"/>于<placeName key="PL000000058935">晉水</placeName>之西山，小塔至今存焉。</p>
<p xml:id="pT50p0858a2601"><lb
ed="T" n="0858a26"/>系曰：<persName key="A009945">塵<roleName>師</roleName></persName>捐捨，詎能愈其精進乎？脫落浮<lb
ed="T" n="0858a27"/>榮，豈能勝其義解<ptr rend="display:none;" type="glossary" target="#g544"/>乎？若然者，不可以一名<lb
ed="T" n="0858a28"/>名矣。厥猶瞻蔔<ptr type="glossary" target="#g525"/><anchor xml:id="beg0858sgsz15"/>華<anchor xml:id="end0858sgsz15"/>焉，色黃而<anchor xml:id="beg0858003"/><choice resp="sgsz"><sic>矣</sic><corr>美</corr></choice><anchor xml:id="end0858003"/>，則真金<lb
ed="T" n="0858a29"/>謝其色；香芬而遠，則牛頭<ptr type="glossary" target="#g1599"/>愧其香。多名生<pb ed="T" n="0858b" xml:id="T50.2061.0858b"/><lb
ed="T" n="0858b01"/>乎一體者，其<persName key="A009945">塵<roleName>公</roleName></persName>歟！</p>
